{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":13147,"duration_api_ms":13035,"num_turns":5,"result":"## REST Endpoints\n\n| HTTP Method | URL Path | Handler Method |\n|---|---|---|\n| `GET` | `/api/users` | `UserController.listUsers()` |\n| `GET` | `/api/users/{id}` | `UserController.getUser()` |\n| `POST` | `/api/users` | `UserController.createUser()` |\n| `DELETE` | `/api/users/{id}` | `UserController.deleteUser()` |\n\nNote: `UserService.update()` exists but has **no corresponding endpoint** in the controller — there is no `PUT /api/users/{id}` mapping.\n\n## Module Dependencies\n\nThe user module depends on two other modules:\n\n1. **`com.acme.auth`** — `AuthService` is used in `UserController` to validate tokens on every request.\n2. **`com.acme.notification`** — `NotificationService` is used in `UserService` to send emails on user create (`sendWelcome`), update (`sendUserUpdated`), and delete (`sendAccountDeleted`).","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"b040fd0d-b28f-41ea-b5b1-9abf48c19b32","total_cost_usd":0.0832585,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":7502,"cache_read_input_tokens":45192,"output_tokens":550,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":7502,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6[1m]":{"inputTokens":5,"outputTokens":550,"cacheReadInputTokens":45192,"cacheCreationInputTokens":7502,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.0832585,"contextWindow":1000000,"maxOutputTokens":64000}},"permission_denials":[],"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"4ff8097c-3229-45e8-abc9-cd186c325d4c"}
